          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>13</td>
          <td>March and Chatteris Talking Newspaper Association</td>
          <td>providing recorded tapes and tactile reading matter to visually impaired and physically handicapped people in the local community.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>Mind Resource Centre Volunteer Group</td>
